    About Us: Discover Our Story and Commitment
We have been in business since 1988 and have been serving Long Island ever since. We are a family-owned business where personal involvement matters. Led by our founder, James Moore, and his eldest son, Nick, we ensure each project receives the attention it deserves, guaranteeing top-notch service for our clients. We are a general contracting business located in Levittown, New York, and serve many towns on Long Island.

Our Specializations
We specialize in Masonry, Paver Sealing, Concrete, and Pressure Washing. We are dedicated to providing the best service possible to our clients. We are fully licensed and insured.

Our Commitment
We are proud to be a part of the Long Island community and look forward to working with you. We understand the process can be overwhelming, but we are here to help. We will work with you to make sure your project is completed on time and within budget. We are committed to providing excellent customer service and will work with you every step of the way.
